_sText:
Final version of my hedgemaze map
Moved some hedges
made 2cnd floor walkways wider
added walkways and ladders to other side
Added a covered bridge in middle, this really helped flesh the level out for 2cnd floor battles.
upped spawns from 24 to 32
add middle ladder on one side
On my server it is well liked, gets nominated often and never see's a successful RTV map switch
Any feed back is very welcome and appreciated, even negative feedback, I can take it.
However if your going to post that it sucks, at least try and have a reason or suggestion for me
